(Marc) tekereza kuri ibi
[kurasa ku ntego] twavuzeho.

182
00:09:05,374 --> 00:09:07,073
Tekereza kurugero rwa Canon.

183
00:09:07,074 --> 00:09:10,424
Tekereza kuri ubu bushobozi
buri bwose ukwabo.

184
00:09:10,425 --> 00:09:13,249
ni iki bwakora?
ni ibihe biburanga?

185
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:15,701
Rero ukeneye gutandukanya,
ahantu ukra ikoranabuhanga, mu buryo bumwe,

186
00:09:15,702 --> 00:09:18,254
n'uburyo bishobora gukoreshwa ku isoko,
ukabitandukanya.

187
00:09:18,255 --> 00:09:22,025
Ukareba ikoranabuhanga
rijyanye nabyo.

188
00:09:22,026 --> 00:09:24,434
Mu ntambwe ikurikiyeho, wavuga uti,

189
00:09:24,435 --> 00:09:29,627
"Ndongera mpuze ikoranabuhanga ryanjye
n'ibindi rishobora kuba ryakoreshwa ku isoko"

190
00:09:30,617 --> 00:09:35,364
Rero ni ibanze mukumva,
ibintu byose byakorwa n'ibicuruzwa byawe

191
00:09:35,365 --> 00:09:39,025
ariko nanone bijyendera kukuba
wabasha kubona amahirwe.

192
00:09:39,026 --> 00:09:41,088
iyo nayo si impano,

193
00:09:41,089 --> 00:09:44,522
bivugako ugomba kujya hariya hanze
ukajyerajyeza kumva aho byakoreshwa

194
00:09:44,523 --> 00:09:47,756
ni ureba kubwoko bw'iki kibazo
gishimishije

195
00:09:47,757 --> 00:09:50,935
ndetse cyinahemba neza,
iyo ubashije kugitsinda,

196
00:09:50,936 --> 00:09:52,455
- mu gace gakurikiraho -

197
00:09:52,456 --> 00:09:57,410
Ariko kuri ubu, bitekerezeho
nk'uburyo bwo gutanduknya ukongera ugahuza,

198
00:09:57,411 --> 00:09:59,214
kuko nyuma yaho noneho ushobora gusobanukirwa

199
00:09:59,215 --> 00:10:02,485
kampani yawe, ifatizo ryo
gushinga kampani yawe muburyo bwiza.

200
00:10:02,486 --> 00:10:05,304
Ndacyeka ko ari kimwe mubigize
imitekerereze ya ba rwiyemezamirimo 

201
00:10:05,305 --> 00:10:07,206
kugerageza bakanatekereza indi mimaro.

202
00:10:07,207 --> 00:10:10,191
Abantu benshi batekereza,
bakana zana ibintu by'ikoranabuhanga

203
00:10:10,192 --> 00:10:14,074
Hanyuma bakaguma,
kuhantu hambere ryakoreshwa batekereje.

204
00:10:14,075 --> 00:10:15,874
Mujyihe, ikiri kudutera imbaraga zo gukora

205
00:10:15,875 --> 00:10:18,821
ari ukubitekerezaho neza
tukareba n'ahandi byakoreshwa.

206
00:10:18,821 --> 00:10:21,354
Icyo ni icyintu cy'ingirakamaro
kuko hakozwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi

207
00:10:21,354 --> 00:10:24,552
bwagaragaje ko abantu,
bazi neza ibyo kwihangira imirimo

208
00:10:24,553 --> 00:10:26,408
baba babasha kumenya ibi.

209
00:10:26,409 --> 00:10:28,448
baba bashobora kurebera ibintu
mumfuruka zitandukanye

210
00:10:28,448 --> 00:10:31,448
bakajyerageza kumva
aho byakoreshwa neza kurusha ahandi.

211
00:10:31,448 --> 00:10:33,968
Ibyo rero byo kujya hirya no hino no kuganira n'abantu
bigomba kukuyobora,

212
00:10:33,969 --> 00:10:36,503
Kukubona amahirwe akomeye cyane

213
00:10:36,504 --> 00:10:39,043
ukajyera no kucyo twita 
"application y'ubwicanyi"

214
00:10:39,044 --> 00:10:41,483
atari muburyo bubi,
ahubwo muburyo bwiza.

215
00:10:41,484 --> 00:10:43,995
kubera ko igomba kuba ari application

216
00:10:43,996 --> 00:10:46,405
Ushobora gukuramo 
amafaranga menshi kurusha ahandi.

217
00:10:46,406 --> 00:10:48,405
-Ikigarurira isoko ryose.
-ibyo nibyo.

218
00:10:48,406 --> 00:10:51,593
Aho ufite ubushobozi n'amahirwe
byo gukuraho abo muhanganye. (araseka)

219
00:10:52,543 --> 00:10:55,629
Reka turebe kuri rimwe,
uyu ni umugozi ukoze hifashishijwe carbon

220
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:59,800
Nazo zakozwe na NASA kugirango
Barinde banabone uko batuza  za satellite mukirere

221
00:10:59,801 --> 00:11:02,804
bikoze mukantu gatoya,
kataremereye.

222
00:11:02,805 --> 00:11:06,057
Byakozwe muri za 50
ariko byatwaye imyaka 15

223
00:11:06,058 --> 00:11:07,958
Kugirango umuntu abone ko

224
00:11:07,959 --> 00:11:11,804
Ikintu byakoreshwa gikomeye
Ari ukwifashishwa nk'ibikoresho bya siporo.

225
00:11:11,805 --> 00:11:15,681
Muri iyi minsi, zikoreshwa ahantu hose,
mubikoresho bya siporo,

226
00:11:15,682 --> 00:11:17,267
Nyamara byatwaye igihe kirekire.

227
00:11:17,268 --> 00:11:20,963
Rero ni utekreza kukibazo nk'iki
turi kuvugaho nonaha,

228
00:11:21,955 --> 00:11:24,445
niba koko uzi neza
kubona amahirwe 

229
00:11:24,446 --> 00:11:26,648
ibi birakomeye cyane
mugushinga umushinga wawe,

230
00:11:26,649 --> 00:11:29,837
Kuko bisobanuye ko ko ugomba
kuba ari wowe wambere ubona

231
00:11:29,838 --> 00:11:33,668
Iyi mimaro myiza cyane,
yagufasha gukuza kampani yawe

232
00:11:33,669 --> 00:11:37,317
Muri rusange, ni ubitekerezaho,
bifite imimaro ibiri ikomeye

233
00:11:37,318 --> 00:11:40,060
Icyambere, amahirwe y'isoko,
atuma ubona ahantu wakwagukira

234
00:11:40,061 --> 00:11:41,664
akaba ariho wubaka umushinga wawe

235
00:11:41,665 --> 00:11:46,299
bikanatanga ishusho y'umwirondoro
w'umushinga cyagwa kampani yawe

236
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:49,683
Uko abandi bantu bakubona,
ni uko nawe wibona ubwawe,

237
00:11:49,684 --> 00:11:51,791
rero ni kimwe
mubyemezo by'ingenzi

238
00:11:51,792 --> 00:11:54,121
uzafata nka rwiyemezamirimo

239
00:11:54,122 --> 00:11:56,860
(Marc) kugirango ubashe kubona
umumaro ukomeye,

240
00:11:56,861 --> 00:11:59,889
urashaka kubona
ni ayahe mahirwe ari hanze hariya

241
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:01,677
Ntago ari ibintu byizana.

242
00:12:01,678 --> 00:12:03,924
Ikibazo nkeka ko gishimishije ni

243
00:12:03,925 --> 00:12:06,132
Ni ayahe mahirwe
udahita ubona ako kanya?

244
00:12:06,133 --> 00:12:07,902
Ni  iki wakora kujyira ngo ubone

245
00:12:07,903 --> 00:12:10,540
Ayo mahirwe,
agutegereje?

246
00:12:11,147 --> 00:12:13,609
Icyo rero ntago aricyo,
turi buganireho uyu munsi--

247
00:12:13,610 --> 00:12:16,965
Ariko ni cyo tuzavugaho mu gace gataha
Aho Marc azabafasha kumva.

248
00:12:16,966 --> 00:12:19,643
Ibyo bizaba ari 2.2, tubone icyo gihe.
